*Majke* su uvek tu da nas podrže. (Mothers are always there to support us.)

*Majci* je bilo važno da joj se sin vrati sa putovanja. (It was important to the mother that her son returned from the trip.)

*Majkama* je prijalo da ponekad provedu vreme sa svojom decom. (Mothers enjoyed spending time with their children sometimes.)

Deca obično imaju veliko poštovanje prema *majkama*. (Children usually have a lot of respect for their mothers.)

*Majčinstvo* je jedno od najzahtevnijih poslova. (Motherhood is one of the most demanding jobs.)